rows.name:
If you're looking for Lilio and the
others, I've got them helping out at
the port to build up their strength.

rows.label: tlk006401_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Hauling cargo, checking manifests,
mooring Divine Beasts, and so on.

rows.label: tlk006401_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Salvaging requires stamina
and focus. There's no better
training for it, right?

rows.label: tlk006401_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Now it's just a matter of
how much they can endure.
